This is a migration wrapper around `/discover`.

## Wrapper Behavior

1. Capture the request as an `IntentRecord`.
2. Focus the conversation on user pain, goals, non-goals, hypotheses, and the narrowest useful wedge.
3. Tell the user the canonical command is `/discover` and keep the state in `.kstack/state`.
